query:
SELECT
    q.s AS "species!: SpeciesGroup",
    COALESCE(ARRAY_AGG(q.w), '{}') AS "weeks!"
FROM
    (
        SELECT
            (UNNEST(species_group_ids)) AS s,
            (DATE_PART('week', start_timestamp)::INT) AS w
        FROM
            hauls
        WHERE
            gear_group_id = $1
        GROUP BY
            (UNNEST(species_group_ids)),
            (DATE_PART('week', start_timestamp)::INT)
        HAVING
            COUNT(*) > $2
    ) q
GROUP BY
    q.s
